creator: Yuichi Uchida
descriptionHtml:
Join us in collecting opinions and suggestions! Sugggesto is a free opinion gathering and polling app is a place where you can gather opinions on the latest news and topics of the world in real time. where you can collect opinions on the latest news and topics in real time. to collect opinions on local news, chit-chat, hobbies, personal interests, reviews, and much more. Please take a look. You can make your voice heard to the world. Join Sugggesto.

Create, weigh, and like ballot boxes - Sugggesto are easy to use.

Read other people's opinions, like your favorite ballot boxes, and view your votes in a circle. and you can see at a glance. The opinions that have received the most likes and the ones that have been liked the most will be displayed in a visual circle You can intuitively know what opinions you're getting.

Give your opinion on what you care most about by giving your opinion.

Install the Sugggesto app from Google Play and start your free Sugggesto today!

Sugggesto is a service that can be started anonymously. You can create a ballot box, post opinions, and make favorites, all anonymously. If you like Sugggesto, you can create a Sugggesto account. When you create an account, you have a unique username and no one can impersonate you.
descriptionShort: Sugggesto is a service that allows you to gather opinions in real time.

- Fix to add color to user id

- Fixed a bug where you can post twice in a row with consecutive hits.

title: sugggesto ( Live opinion gathering app )

creator: sugggesto
descriptionHtml:
This is an app that allows you to vote live and ask questions at events.

Sugggesto is more than just a Q&A tool. You can reply and react to questions, and they are visualized and displayed in real time. You can even express your feelings and emotions about the event sessions, so let's share our thoughts and make the event more exciting.

Opinions and Questions
If you have an opinion or question about the session you are currently watching, your opinion or question will be displayed on the screen where the participants are watching live.

Rate Opinions
You can rate an opinion as good or bad. The higher the rating, the larger the opinion will be, and the lower the rating, the smaller the opinion will be.

Reply to an opinion or question
When you reply to an opinion/question, the opinion/question and the reply will be linked and displayed.

Reacting to an opinion or question
When you react to an opinion or question, the reaction will be linked and displayed.

This app does not support the function of creating events at this time. If you want to create an event, please visit the website.
https://app.sugggesto.com

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: - Functionality has been modified for events.
